1775174555178533	command-lattice-dev	itc:v3:AWKTkyTOeZ5M5QAAAAAAQa61bvb1ugAAAAEvAg		item.create	bn-27ve	{"description":"When resolving with maw ws resolve default --keep <side>, the trailing >>>>>>> marker is left in the file. Opening markers (<<<<<<, |||||||, =======) are removed correctly but the closing >>>>>>> <side> (local edits) line remains. Found in command-lattice merging bn-1fj7 into default on 2026-04-02 — mesh_renderer.rs had a stray >>>>>>> default (local edits) at EOF after resolve.","kind":"bug","title":"ws resolve --keep leaves trailing conflict marker"}	blake3:Fish9euoj4CaSXA_zKltcgj54cQWfdftd7URiDzE9mQ
