1775175172603302	maw-dev/0	itc:v3:AWL_JPJM885kQAAAAAAAQf9Xq3vdoAAAAAEsGQ		item.comment	bn-27ve	{"body":"Root cause: parse_file_conflicts inner loop doesn't track <<<<<<<nesting depth. A >>>>>>> line in content (e.g. from previously unresolved conflict markers in stashed content) causes premature break, leaving the actual closing >>>>>>> marker as trailing context. Fix: track nested_depth, only treat >>>>>>> as closing marker at depth 0, and similarly gate ||||||| and ======= transitions on depth 0."}	blake3:cfjZDT1Nx51mmrsRTrC3ZVH8FmZWRyeexYr9EOX2hfI
